<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:19:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着投资者减少与中国的联系，越南扩大芯片封装足迹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/vietnam-expands-chip-packaging-footprint-investors-reduce-china-links-2024-11-12/</link><description>高管们表示，由于与西方的贸易紧张局势，工业活动从中国转移的步伐加快，外国公司正在扩大越南的测试和封装芯片产能，而国内公司则在寻求投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:08:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/vietnam-expands-chip-packaging-footprint-investors-reduce-china-links-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国军工在珠海航展展示升级版直20直升机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-military-displays-upgraded-z-20-helicopter-zhuhai-air-show-2024-11-12/</link><description>Z-20在海上填补中国海军防御潜艇能力缺口的潜力正引起密切关注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 05:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-military-displays-upgraded-z-20-helicopter-zhuhai-air-show-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>空客表示A330neo喷气式飞机的中国认证进展顺利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/airbus-says-a330neo-jet-china-certification-progressing-smoothly-2024-11-12/</link><description>空客中国负责人周二表示，其A330neo喷气式飞机的中国认证工作进展顺利，该宽体机型的首次交付可能于2025年在中国交付。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 05:11:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/airbus-says-a330neo-jet-china-certification-progressing-smoothly-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港建筑巨头变身澳门赌场老板吕志和去世，享年 95 岁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-construction-titan-turned-macau-casino-boss-lui-che-woo-dies-aged-95-2024-11-12/</link><description>赌场大亨吕志和去世，享年 95 岁，他的公司在周一晚间的一份声明中表示，吕志和曾帮助澳门在博彩收入方面超越竞争对手拉斯维加斯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 04:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-construction-titan-turned-macau-casino-boss-lui-che-woo-dies-aged-95-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国商飞称国航是C929宽体客机首个客户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/comac-says-air-china-will-be-launch-customer-c929-widebody-jet-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国商飞周二表示，国航是该中国飞机制造商正在开发的C929宽体飞机的第一个客户，该飞机旨在与空客和波音的双通道机型竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 04:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/comac-says-air-china-will-be-launch-customer-c929-widebody-jet-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>百度通过文本到图像生成器、无代码应用程序构建器增强人工智能阵容</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/baidu-bolsters-ai-lineup-with-text-to-image-generator-no-code-app-builder-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国百度公司周二推出了一系列人工智能技术的新应用程序，其中包括文本到图像生成器和使用户无需编码专业知识即可开发软件应用程序的工具。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 03:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/baidu-bolsters-ai-lineup-with-text-to-image-generator-no-code-app-builder-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市回落，比特币因特朗普的兴奋而飙升至创纪录水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-12/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市走低，美元维持在四个月高点，尽管所有的兴奋都集中在比特币上，因为投资者押注可能受益于唐纳德·特朗普当选的资产，比特币飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 03:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国警方在肇事逃逸袭击造成数人受伤后拘留了一名男子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-police-detain-man-after-hit-and-run-attack-leaves-several-wounded-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国南方城市珠海市一体育中心涉嫌​​肇事逃逸袭击事件，造成多人伤亡，警方逮捕了一名 62 岁男子。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 03:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-police-detain-man-after-hit-and-run-attack-leaves-several-wounded-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>人民币汇率下滑、美元指数上涨，卢比创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/all-time-low-beckons-rupee-slide-yuan-rally-dollar-index-2024-11-12/</link><description>受美元指数上涨和唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统选举中获胜后人民币贬值的影响，印度卢比周二开盘可能创下历史新低。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 02:58:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/all-time-low-beckons-rupee-slide-yuan-rally-dollar-index-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>印度股市小幅走高，IT 股领涨；关注国内通胀数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-shares-set-open-higher-after-three-session-drop-2024-11-12/</link><description>印度信息技术股在连续三个交易日下跌后，周二上涨，提振了国内股市，而投资者则等待当天晚些时候公布的当地通胀数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 02:41:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-shares-set-open-higher-after-three-session-drop-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国商飞将支线飞机更名为C909以进行营销推广</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/old-friend-new-look-chinas-comac-renames-regional-jet-c909-marketing-push-2024-11-12/</link><description>此举使该飞机与这家国有公司其他型号的命名惯例保持一致。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 02:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/old-friend-new-look-chinas-comac-renames-regional-jet-c909-marketing-push-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国双十一结束，电子商务公司报告购物者数量增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-singles-day-wraps-up-with-e-commerce-firms-reporting-growth-shoppers-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国最大的电子商务公司阿里巴巴集团表示，今年双十一销售期间销售额“强劲增长”，购物者数量“创纪录”，为期数周的活动于周一午夜结束。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 02:13:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-singles-day-wraps-up-with-e-commerce-firms-reporting-growth-shoppers-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国刺激担忧和供应过剩前景而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-hold-their-ground-after-falling-china-stimulus-2024-11-12/</link><description>由于投资者对中国最新刺激计划的失望和供应过剩担忧以及美元走强打压市场，油价周二下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 02:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-hold-their-ground-after-falling-china-stimulus-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>讲解员：什么是中国的光棍节？如何庆祝？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-is-chinas-singles-day-how-is-it-celebrated-2024-11-11/</link><description>黑色星期五？不。网络星期一？没有。黄金日？绝对不是。世界上最大的购物活动每年都会在中国举行，这天被称为“光棍节”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 23:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-is-chinas-singles-day-how-is-it-celebrated-2024-11-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特朗普推动的记录没有动力或债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-11-11/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 22:15:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-11-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>